title: Sky's Tacos
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A taco/burrito eatery with a menu that includes a dedicated section of veggie and vegan items (tacos, nachos, burritos, and a veggie burger). Has vegan "meat" that's made from soy protein/TVP. Tortilla chips are made in-house. Order at the counter, and food is brought to your table. Causal with plenty of seating. Note: reported to use the same grill for all orders.
